RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select contract_ref_no, user_ref_no, counterparty, branch, latest_event_seq_no, contract_ccy from (select contract_ref_no, user_ref_no, counterparty, branch, latest_event_seq_no, contract_ccy from oltbs_contract a where exists (select 1 from smvws_user_branches b where a.branch = b.branch_code and a.branch = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH and a.branch in (select branch_code from smvws_user_branches where user_id = GLOBAL.USER_ID)) union (select a.contract_ref_no, c.user_ref_no, c.counterparty, a.branch, a.event_seq_no, a.currency from oltbs_contract_adj_master a, oltbs_contract c where a.branch = c.branch AND a.contract_ref_no = c.contract_ref_no))
select ccy_code, ccy_name from cytms_ccy_defn where ccy_code = ? and record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A'
select branch_code from oltms_branch where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A'

SELECT account_number , c.ac_gl_desc , c.ac_gl_ccy, a.amount_type, b.amount_tag FROM oltms_ac_transaction_category a, oltms_account_type b , oltbs_account c WHERE a.amount_type = b.amount_type AND c.ac_gl_no = a.account_number AND a.record_stat = 'O' AND a.auth_stat = 'A' AND b.record_stat = 'O' AND b.auth_stat = 'A' AND b.amount_tag in (SELECT DISTINCT amt_tag FROM oltms_product_event_acct_entry WHERE product_code = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND event_code = 'CADJ') AND a.account_number in (SELECT ac_gl_no FROM oltbs_account ac WHERE (ac_gl_rec_status = 'O' AND auth_stat = 'A') AND (ac_or_gl = 'G' OR (ac_or_gl = 'A' AND branch_code = ?)))

SELECT account_number , c.ac_gl_desc , c.ac_gl_ccy, a.amount_type, b.amount_tag FROM oltms_ac_transaction_category a, oltms_account_type b, oltbs_account c WHERE a.amount_type = b.amount_type AND c.ac_gl_no = a.account_number AND a.record_stat = 'O' AND a.auth_stat = 'A' AND b.record_stat = 'O' AND b.auth_stat = 'A' AND b.amount_tag in (SELECT DISTINCT amt_tag FROM oltms_product_event_acct_entry WHERE product_code = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND event_code = 'CADJ') AND a.account_number in (SELECT ac_gl_no FROM oltbs_account ac WHERE (ac_gl_rec_status = 'O' AND auth_stat = 'A') AND (ac_or_gl = 'G' OR (ac_or_gl = 'A' AND branch_code = ?)))

select component, description from lftm_product_fee where product_code = sypks_utils.get_product(?) union select component, component_description from lftm_product_iccf where product = sypks_utils.get_product(?) union select field_name, field_desc from oltm_static_field_vals where field_type in ('ESC1', 'ESC2', 'ESC3', 'ESC6') and auth_stat = 'A' and record_stat = 'O'
